{
  "info": {
    "name": "Sirion CLM API (Modeled)",
    "description": "MODELED representation of the Sirion (SirionLabs) CLM Business API & Integrations surface. NOT copied from an official public reference - Sirion's API reference is gated behind tenant authentication and access is enterprise/contract-provisioned. Authentication is OAuth 2.0 client credentials (CONFIRMED); the base host {{tenant}}.sirioncloud.com, the token URL, and all paths are MODELED. Replace {{tenant}} with your Sirion subdomain and set {{clientId}}/{{clientSecret}}.",
